homeTitle: Welcome to the NIST/CDC Vital Records CDA Validation Suite
homeContent:
This version of the tool is used to test the HL7 CDA® R2 Implementation Guide:Vital Records Death Reporting,Release 1 STU 2 -US RealmL

This version currently supports:

  • CDC CDA XML

The following browsers are supported: Internet Explorer versions 8 and 9, Firefox, and Chrome. Recommended browsers are Internet Explorer 9, Firefox and Chrome.
